🔹 **Bulk-forming**: Safest long-term. Psyllium, methylcellulose. Need adequate fluids

🔹 **Osmotic**: PEG (best tolerated), lactulose (also for hepatic encephalopathy), Mg-based (rapid)

🔹 **Stimulant**: Short-term only. Senna, bisacodyl. Risk of dependency

🔹 **Stool softeners**: Docusate. Better for prevention than treatment

🔹 **Contraindications**: Bowel obstruction, acute abdomen, GI bleeding`,
